  "title": "Sales & Marketing Executive #76912",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Food Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales & Marketing Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Senoko</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon to Fri 9AM – 6PM, Sat 9AM – 1PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $2,800 + Transport Allowance + Petrol Claims + AWS + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Formulate and execute sales strategies to meet and exceed sales targets</li><li>Conduct market analysis to identify new opportunities and stay updated on industry trends.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients to ensure customer satisfaction</li><li>Plan and implement marketing campaigns across various channels, including digital and traditional media</li><li>Identify and pursue new sales leads, convert prospects into loyal customers</li><li>Enhance brand awareness through targeted promotional activities and events</li><li>Monitor and report on sales performance, providing insights and recommendations for improvement</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Sales, Marketing or relevant discipline</li><li>At least 1 year of Sales experience would be preferred</li><li>Prior experience in the seafood/food manufacturing industry would be a plus</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76912 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
